Definition: an arctic atmospheric condition with clouds over snow produce a uniform whiteness and objects are difficult to see
Example: occurs when the light reflected off the snow equals the light coming through the clouds
Synonyms: snow, an, arctic, atmospheric, condition, with, clouds, over, produce, a, uniform, whiteness, and, objects, are, difficult, to, see, occurs, when, the, light, reflected, off, equals, coming, through
Category: noun.phenomenon
